org.treetank.bucket

Class RevisionRootBucket

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.treetank.bucket.RevisionRootBucket
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBucket, IReferenceBucket

    public final class RevisionRootBucket
extends Object
implements IReferenceBucket

    RevisionRootBucket

    Revision root bucket holds a reference to the name bucket as well as the static data-bucket tree.

    Author:
    Sebastian Graf, University of Konstanz, Marc Kramis, University of Konstanz
